title: I decided to speedrun Duck Life and pleasantly annihilated every other duck
author: EazySpeezy
description:
Duck Life is a game that I never thought I'd speedrun, but I definitely don't regret it. This game is in a class of its own.

Watch live at: http://twitch.tv/EazySpeezy

▶ Twitter: https://twitter.com/EazySpeezy
▶ Discord: https://discord.gg/Fz6Dtdq

Watch the world record run here: https://youtu.be/jkwzJMapPeU

My channel generally focuses on a more casual side of speedruns. With these videos I want to show off cool speedruns, explain how they work, and entertain. Hopefully you enjoy the content and maybe even take up speedrunning yourself, because it is truly a lot of fun!

#EazySpeezy #DuckLife #Speedrun
